      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just that though. it's more like... everything feels so heavy and pointless. like i'm just taking up space that someone else could actually use. it feels like there's no point in trying to force connections when everything just feels so empty. sometimes it just seems easier to just stop existing than to keep pretending i matter.",
